title: Arts and Crafts Homes - Spring 2016
description:
English | 76 pages | PDF | 21.9 MB




Inspiring Arts & Crafts Homes Enthusiasts. Our mission is to celebrate the revival of quality and craftsmanship in homebuilding, going beyond the narrow definition of American Arts & Crafts as a "style" confined to the early decades of the 20th century. Each issue is a portfolio of the best work in new construction, restoration, and interpretive design, presented through intelligent writing and beautiful photographs
